1. Nf3 f5 2. d4 Nf6 3. Bf4 e6 4. e3 b6 5. Bd3 Bb7 6. O-O Be7 7. h3 O-O 8. c4 d6 9. Nc3 h6 10. Bh2 Ne4 11. Bxe4 fxe4 12. Nd2 d5 13. Qg4 Bc8 14. Be5 Bf6 15. f4 c5 16. Qh5 Bb7 17. Nb5 cxd4 18. Nxd4 Qe7 19. Qg4 Bc8 20. Rac1 Bd7 21. Qg3 Bxe5 22. fxe5 Rxf1+ 23. Rxf1 Nc6 24. cxd5 Nxd4 25. exd4 exd5 26. Rc1 Rc8 27. Rxc8+ Bxc8 28. Qc3 Ba6 29. Qc6 Bb7 30. Qb5 Kh7 31. Nf1 Qg5 32. b4 Qc1 33. Qd7 e3 34. Qf5+ Kg8 35. Qd3 Qa1 36. Kh2 e2 37. Qxe2 Qxd4 38. a3 Qe4 39. Ng3 Qf4 40. Qh5 d4 41. Qe8+ Kh7 42. Qd7 Ba8 43. Qxa7 Bd5 { 0-1 Black wins. } 44. Qd7 { [%csl Gf5][%cal Gd7f5] } (44. Qa6 Qf2 45. Qe2) (44. Qxg7+ Kxg7 { [%csl Gh2,Gg3][%cal Gf4h2,Gg3h5] }) 0-1


[Event "Blundering Lecture: Brain Freeze: Grischuk - Caruana"]
[Date "2019.06.25"]
[White "Grischuk"]
