[StudyName "My biggest win ever (in OTB play)"]
[ChapterName "Rosen, Eric - Ivanisevic, Ivan"]
[ChapterURL "https://lichess.org/study/oG1IVo1W/8bmb4rX9"]

{ Before the round, I thought I was going to play Kacheishvili, so I looked him
up and found what he plays against the English. I spent 5-10 minutes loooking
over a certain line, until they posted pairings, and I realized I was playing
Ivanisevic. I had no time to look up Ivanisevic, but luckily he played the
same line I was preparing for Kacheishvili. }
1. c4 c5 2. Nf3 Nc6 3. Nc3 g6 4. e3 { [%csl Gd4][%cal Gd2d4,Gd4d5] } (4. g3 { This is probably what I would have played if I hadn't looked at
Kacheishvili's game against the English }) 4... Bg7 5. d4 d6 6. d5 Na5 (6... Bxc3+ 7. bxc3) (6... Ne5) 7. Bd3 (7. Bd2) 7... Nf6 8. O-O O-O 9. a3 b6 10. b4 Nb7 11. Bb2 Bg4 (11... cxb4 12. axb4 a5 (12... Bg4 13. Ra6 { reminded me of an
idea in Rosen-Hess 2009 }) 13. Nd4) 12. Be2 Rc8 13. b5 e5 14. Nd2 h5 15. a4 Na5 16. Bxg4 hxg4 17. f4 gxf3 18. Rxf3 Nh7 19. Qe2 f5 20. e4 f4 { [%csl Gf2,Gg4][%cal Gc3d1,Gd1f2,Gf2g4,Gh2h3,Gd2f1,Gf1h2,Gf3d3] } 21. Nd1 Qd7 22. Nf2 Nf6 23. Rfa3 Bh6 24. Bc3 Rf7 25. h3 Rh7 26. Nf3 Rf8 27. Bxa5 bxa5 28. Nh2 { I offered a draw somewhere around here } 28... Bg5 29. Nfg4 Nh5 30. Nf1 Rff7 31. Rf3 Bd8 32. Raa3 Ng7 33. Qd2 Ne8 34. Qe2 Rh4 { [%cal Ge2d2,Gd2e2] } 35. Nfh2 Rfh7 36. Qe1 Kh8 37. Qc3 Ng7 38. Kf2 Nh5 39. Qd3 Ng3 40. Kg1 { [%csl Gg3] } 40... Kg8 41. Ra2 R7h5 42. Rb2 Rg5 43. Rb1 Qg7 44. Kf2 { [%csl Gg5,Gh4,Gg3] } 44... Nf5 45. Ke1 (45. exf5 gxf5) 45... Nd4 46. Rf2 Qh7 47. Kd2 Rgh5 48. Nf3 Nxf3+ 49. Qxf3 Rg5 { [%csl Gg4] } 50. Kc2 Qd7 51. Rb3 Qh7 52. Rb1 Kg7 53. Rbf1 Qh5 54. Qb3 Rgxg4 55. hxg4 Rxg4 56. b6 { [%csl Gd7,Rg7][%cal Gb3b5,Gb5d7] } 56... axb6 57. Qb5 Bh4 58. Qd7+ Kh6 59. Rh1 { [%csl Gh6][%cal Gh1h6,Rd7g4,Rd7d6] } 59... Rg3 (59... Bxf2 { [%csl Gf2,Gg2,Gg1][%cal Gh4f2,Gg4g2,Gg2g3,Gg3g1] } 60. Rxh5+ Kxh5 61. Qxd6 Bd4 62. Qxb6 Rxg2+ { [%csl Gc2][%cal Gg2g3,Gg3g2,Gg2g1,Gc2d3,Gd3e2,Ge2f3,Ge2f1] } 63. Kd3 Rg3+ 64. Ke2 Rg2+ 65. Kf3 Rg3+ { [%csl Gf2][%cal Gd4f2] } 66. Ke2 Rg2+ 67. Kf1 { [%csl Gf1] } 67... Rg1+) 60. Qxd6 Re3 { offered draw } { [%csl Gh6] } 61. Qf8+ Kg5 (61... Kh7 62. g3 (62. g4 Qxg4 63. Qe7+)) 62. Qe7+ Kg4 63. Rxh4+ Qxh4 64. Qxh4+ Kxh4 65. d6 { [%cal Gd6d8] } 65... Kg3 66. Rd2 f3 67. gxf3 Rxf3 68. Rd3 { 1-0 Black resigns. } 1-0


